provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio.html — Python asyncio module documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/queues.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: wave 255 theme — asyncio.Queue method co_varnames (complementing prior co_varnames coverage in extra125). NEW in extra126: asyncio.Queue.put.__code__.co_varnames[0]=='self'; asyncio.Queue.put.__code__.co_varnames[1]=='item'; asyncio.Queue.put.__code__.co_argcount==2; asyncio.Queue.put.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==3; asyncio.Queue.get.__code__.co_varnames[0]=='self'; asyncio.Queue.get.__code__.co_argcount==1; asyncio.Queue.get.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==2; asyncio.Queue.put_nowait.__code__.co_varnames[0]=='self'; asyncio.Queue.put_nowait.__code__.co_varnames[1]=='item'; asyncio.Queue.put_nowait.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==2; asyncio.Queue.task_done.__code__.co_varnames.__len__()==1; asyncio.Queue.get_nowait.__code__.co_varnames[0]=='self'; asyncio.Queue.get_nowait.__code__.co_argcount==1. All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Queue.put.__code__.co_varnames == ('self', 'item', 'putter'). put is defined as 'async def put(self, item)' with 2 positional params (co_argcount==2); co_varnames has 3 entries: self, item, and the local variable putter used for waiting. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Queue.get.__code__.co_varnames == ('self', 'getter'). get is defined as 'async def get(self)' with 1 positional param (co_argcount==1); co_varnames has 2 entries: self plus local getter used for waiting. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Queue.put_nowait.__code__.co_varnames == ('self', 'item'). put_nowait is defined as 'def put_nowait(self, item)' with 2 positional params; co_varnames has exactly 2 entries (no locals beyond params). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Queue.task_done.__code__.co_varnames.__len__() == 1. task_done is defined as 'def task_done(self)' with only self; co_varnames has exactly 1 entry. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

